	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "7 In spite of fuerat in this text Titius must still have been a Tribune of the Soldiers in this year, since it was the year of the formation of the legion in which he served (Bell. Alex. 50.3; 53.4). See Bell. Afr. 28.2." .
